summary: 19110204An ordinance authorizing and directing the Water Department to lay a 2-inch water main from the intersection of Alki Avenue with Spokane Avenue from the west to the intersection of West Spokane Street with the alley in block 1, Seaboard Addition to West Seattle; thence south along said alley through blocks 1, 2, and 3, Seaboard Addition to West Charlestown Street.
